name: I Hate Suzie
overview: Suzie Pickles, a star on the wane, has her whole life upended when her phone is hacked and a photo of her emerges in an extremely compromising position.

seasons.name: I Hate Suzie Too
seasons.overview: Suzie has a new agent, new PR and a new job – dancing for likes on ‘Dance Crazee’, a reality TV competition that has the Saturday night audience hooked. Having lost everyone that matters to her, Suzie returns to her first love – the public. Battling ex-husband Cob with the help of estranged best friend Naomi, Suzie must try to keep life as stable as possible for her young son Frank, all whilst staying on ‘Dance Crazee’ long enough to finance her new role as single mum and ex-wife.

episodes.name: Shock
episodes.overview: Compromising pictures of Suzie have been hacked from her phone. Her apparently perfect life spectacularly implodes.

episodes.name: Denial
episodes.overview: When no one believes her claim that the sex photos are fake, Suzie parties while her family life hangs in the balance.

episodes.name: Fear
episodes.overview: Working to save her marriage, Suzie agrees that maybe working with the man in question isn't the best idea. Naomi attempts to keep the press at bay.

episodes.name: Shame
episodes.overview: Suzie gives a disastrous interview and struggles to make peace with her own desires.

episodes.name: Bargaining
episodes.overview: Cob decides it's his turn to let loose and Suzie is forced to combine her dinner her producers with Cob's wild night out.

episodes.name: Guilt
episodes.overview: Suzie is on the lookout for a career change and auditions for a new musical. Family politics come to light with Suzie's parents.

episodes.name: Anger
episodes.overview: Suzie tries to keep her cool and focus on balancing work and family. Naomi finds herself struggling.

episodes.name: Acceptance
episodes.overview: Suzie has to come to terms with her situation and make some big decisions. Series finale.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: She's back. And she's dancing. With Cob refusing her access to her son and her relationship with Naomi still dicey, Suzie needs all the friends she can get.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Suzie tries to win everyone's affection by being the real Suzie. If she can recall what that is.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: As the night of the Dance Crazee Xmas final arrives, Suzie is on the edge of glory and disaster.
